<SiteLayout description="Deependra Solanky's writing on products, productivity, technology, and personal projects.">
	<section class="home" aria-labelledby="home-title">
		<div class="container prose home-inner">
			<h1 id="home-title" class="visually-hidden">Deependra Solanky</h1>
			<p class="lead">This is where I write about products, productivity, technology, and the systems we use to get work done.</p>
			<p>Most of my writing begins with something I use or a problem I am trying to understand: a way of organising work, a product decision, or a piece of technology. Writing helps me examine it more carefully and share what I learn along the way.</p>
			<p>I also keep a few personal, open-source projects. They come from problems I wanted to solve for myself and evolve as time and interest allow.</p>
			<p class="home-links"><a href="/blog/">Read my writing</a> <span aria-hidden="true">·</span> <a href="/projects/">Browse projects</a></p>
		</div>
	</section>
</SiteLayout>